        "remarks": "<format type=\"text/markdown\"><![CDATA[\n## Remarks\n\n`SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp` enumerates the opto-electronic transfer function (OETF/EOTF)\ncomponent of CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) as defined in ITU-T H.273. These values\ncorrespond to the `TransferCharacteristics` field of the CICP code.\n\nUse these values with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(SkiaSharp.SKColorspacePrimariesCicp,SkiaSharp.SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp)>\nto create a color space from CICP parameters.\n]]></format>",
        "summary": "Specifies the opto-electronic transfer function component of a CICP color space encoding.",
        "remarksRequired": true
      }
    },
